WARNING: DO NOT IN ANY CIRCUMSTANCE OPERATE THE DEVICE WHILE CONNECTED TO AC POWER

Flash using any of the provided TX/RX headers and GND. Do not connect VCC from the USB-to-serial adapter but power the module using micro USB.

UART Program download port: ESP8266 GND，RX，TX，5V separately connect external TTL Serial module GND，TX，RX，5V, IO0 need with GND connect when download, disconnect the connection between IO0 and GND After the download is complete.